      <p>Subscriptions are billed at the frequency corresponding to your plan (weekly for the 7-Day Plan; monthly for the 30-Day Plan). All plans renew automatically at the end of each commitment period unless cancelled in accordance with Section 7.</p>
      <p>By subscribing, you authorize Pilot to charge your payment method on a recurring basis. All fees are in U.S. dollars. Pilot reserves the right to change plan pricing with advance notice. Continued use after a price change constitutes acceptance of the new pricing.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- §7 -->
