      <h3>8.1 Plan Changes</h3>
      <p>You may request a change between the 7-Day and 30-Day plans at any time. Plan changes take effect at the end of your current commitment period. Your current plan, budgeted rate, and coverage remain in effect until the switch date. On the switch date, a new commitment begins with a new budgeted rate based on the new plan's rolling window. No remaining balance applies to plan switches, as they always occur at a commitment boundary.</p>
      <p>You may cancel a pending plan switch at any time before it executes.</p>

      <h3>8.2 Location Changes</h3>
      <p>You may change your coverage location (zip code or National Average) at any time. Location changes follow the same timing rules as plan changes — the new location takes effect at the end of your current commitment period, at which point your budgeted rate will be recalculated based on the new location.</p>
    </section>

