      <h2>Reimbursements</h2>
      <p>Reimbursements are calculated based on the positive difference between the average retail gasoline price for your selected locale during the coverage period and your budgeted rate, multiplied by the number of gallons purchased (up to your plan's gallon cap). Reimbursements are deposited automatically to your connected account.</p>
      <p>Pilot reserves the right to investigate and deny reimbursement claims that appear fraudulent, erroneous, or inconsistent with normal fueling behavior. Submission of false or inflated claims may result in immediate account termination and recovery of prior reimbursements.</p>
    </section>

